title: Astaanta Martigelinta
subtitle: Samee astaan soo dhaweyn leh oo martida ka caawisa inay si fiican kuu ogaadaan.

photo.title: Sawirka Astaanta
photo.subtitle: Ku dar sawir saaxiibtinimo leh si aad uga caawiso martida inay ku aqoonsadaan
photo.selectPhotoDescription: Dooro sida aad jeceshahay inaad ku darto sawirkaaga
photo.permissionRequired: Ruqsadda maktabadda sawirrada ayaa loo baahan yahay
photo.cameraPermissionRequired: Ruqsadda kaamirka ayaa loo baahan yahay
photo.helpText: Sawir cad oo saaxiibtinimo leh ayaa martida ka caawiya inay dareemaan raaxo marka ay kula buukaan.

bio.title: Adiga ku saabsan
bio.subtitle: Uga sheeg martida adiga iyo waxa kaa dhiga martigale fiican
bio.placeholder: Wadaag wax yar oo ku saabsan adiga, xiisahaaga, iyo waxa aad ka jeceshahay martigelinta martida...
bio.tips: Noqo mid run ah oo soo dhaweyn
bio.minLength: Taariikh nololeedku waa inuu ugu yaraan 50 xaraf yahay
bio.helpText: Taariikh nololeed fikirsan ayaa martida ka caawiya inay ku ogaadaan oo kalsoni dhisa.

details.title: Faahfaahinta Shakhsiga
details.subtitle: Wadaag macluumad aasaasi ah oo ku saabsan adiga

location.title: Goobta
location.helpText: Goobtuhu waxay martida ka caawisaa inay fahmaan aqoontaada maxalliga ah.

occupation.title: Shaqada
occupation.helpText: Wadaagista shaqadaada ayaa martida ka caawiya inay kula xidhiidhaan.

interests.title: Xiisaha
interests.subtitle: Maxaad xamaasad u qabaa? (Dooro ilaa 10)
interests.helpText: Wadaagista xiisahaaga ayaa martida ka caawiya inay kula xiriiraan heer shakhsi ah.
